                <div class="text-content">
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Goal</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We aimed to use the responses to each question as a gauge on how successful each question was in garnering the information on the opportunities for Kim to direct future department efforts and community outreach.</p>
