                <div class="text-content">
                  <h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Why?</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">After conducting our first prototype, we realized that our <strong>target audience was too broad</strong>. Having all Boston citizens be the audience resulted in a very varied interest in data and goals. We checked in with Kim, and decided to <strong>narrow in on community organizations</strong> that may already be dealing with data or would like help accessing it.</p>
